    <h1>21 Ways to Get More Google Reviews (Without Begging)</h1>
    <p class="description">21 tested strategies to grow your Google review count on autopilot. In-person, digital, and automated methods. Policy-compliant. Updated March 2026.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
